testbit
=======
A test server for bitbit.

Building testbit
----------------
Run

	$ make

in the root directory. If the server is desired, it can be compiled by issuing

	$ make everything

instead.


Installing testbit
------------------
testbitn needs a user called "testbit" to be present. On Linux it is preferably
created by

	# useradd --system                 \
                  --no-create-home         \
		  --comment "testbit user" \
		  --home-dir /dev/null     \
		  --shell /sbin/nologin    \
		  testbit
